The paper describes the integration of a QBF solver into a massively parallel SAT solver, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The use of parallel computing also suggests a focus on distributed systems (cs.DS) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the experimental evaluation of performance suggests a focus on software engineering (cs.SE).
